org.mitre.provenance.plusobject

Class PLUSEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.AbstractDirectedEdge
      • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.PLUSEdge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourcedObject

    public class PLUSEdge
extends AbstractDirectedEdge
    This class models an edge in a provenance graph. This class is ONLY for provenance edges

    The type of a PLUSEdge must always be one of the enumerated strings in this class. For any other type of edge (bearing non- provenance semantics) use NonProvenanceEdge

    Author:
    DMALLEN
    See Also:
    NonProvenanceEdge
